[gd_scene load_steps=12 format=3]

; Hero block: downtown LA tuned for real-time photorealism — AgX tonemap, SDFGI
; global illumination, screen-space reflections + indirect light, volumetric
; fog, golden-hour sun with soft shadows, and a DoF + auto-exposure camera.
; PhotorealTuner upgrades the generated facades/asphalt to reflective PBR. This
; is the proof-of-look before scaling the treatment city-wide.

